{"id":262453,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/外媒称中国用天网监视西藏/","date":"2012-11-11T11:00:28Z","modified":"2012-11-11T11:00:28Z","title":"外媒称中国用天网监视西藏","content":"<p>英国媒体《每日电讯报》报导称中国正用高度机密的“天网”监视西藏及周边省份。报导引用西藏自治区副主席洛桑江村的话称，他们能在事故发生两分钟内启动紧急救援。他说，“我们不想看到此类事故（自焚），我们不希望任何人破坏西藏的快乐和平。对于当地人，我们正在检查身份证；对于游客，我们有检查站和安全检查。”根据文章上下文，所谓的“天网”其实就是已实施多年的网格化管理系统。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/2576b3a4/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/viral/sendEmail.cfm?lang=en&#038;title=%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A9%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F11%2F11%2F096219%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A9%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F11%2F11%2F096219%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/149379613953/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2576b3a4/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/149379613953/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2576b3a4/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/149379613953/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2576b3a4/a2t.img\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=hwJ2kSNDUtg:Bg2KKLYtKww:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=hwJ2kSNDUtg:Bg2KKLYtKww:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburn